<sect1 id="kapp-settings">
<title
>Настройки</title>

<screenshot
> <screeninfo
>Это снимок диалога настроек</screeninfo
> <mediaobject
> <imageobject
> <imagedata fileref="settings.png" format="PNG"/> </imageobject
